      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretna%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Gretna sits just 8 miles south of the Florida‑Georgia border, placing it close to the state line.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
