      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretna%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The city’s coordinates are 30°36′56″N 84°39′45″W, locating it in west‑central Gadsden County on the Panhandle.",
